; Live liveness policy: every tool call must return a result within 5s.
; Used by `mo watch` — the silence problem (premortem #1) is exactly this:
; if the server is called and then goes quiet, a synthetic tick must cross
; the window and BOLT, even though no further wire event ever arrives.

on tool_called as $tool:
    EXPECT tool_result for $tool
    WINDOW 5000
